title: Dániel Lukács
text:
Dániel Lukács (born 3 April 1996) is a <a href="Hungarian%20people">Hungarian</a> <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player who currently plays for <a href="Kecskem%C3%A9ti%20TE">Kecskeméti TE</a>
Career.
Budapest Honvéd.
On 28 November 2015, Lukács played his first match for Budapest Honvéd in a 3-2 win against <a href="B%C3%A9k%C3%A9scsaba%201912%20El%C5%91re">Békéscsaba</a> in the <a href="Nemzeti%20Bajnoks%C3%A1g%20I">Hungarian League</a>.
Club statistics.
"Updated to games played as of 19 May 2019."
